---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Real Results - Greenfield Platform"
  description="Real results across every context: SaaS applications built in days, 15-year systems modernized safely, teams achieving 100x productivity."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Real Results
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            These aren't theoretical benefits. This is what teams are achieving in production right now.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Results Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <!-- Production Speed -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900 to-green-800 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-8.293l-3-3a1 1 0 00-1.414 0l-3 3a1 1 0 001.414 1.414L9 9.414V13a1 1 0 102 0V9.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">Production Speed</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">SaaS Applications in Days</h3>
                <p class="text-green-100 mb-3">
                  Complete SaaS platforms with user management, payments, and core functionality deployed to production.
                </p>
                <div class="text-sm text-green-200">
                  <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                    <span>Traditional Approach:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold">6-12 months</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>With Greenfield Platform:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-green-400">3-7 days</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-green-200 text-sm">
                "We launched our MVP in 4 days and had paying customers by day 6." - Sarah Chen, Startup Founder
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Legacy Transformation -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-blue-800 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 2a1 1 0 011 1v2.101a7.002 7.002 0 0111.601 2.566 1 1 0 11-1.885.666A5.002 5.002 0 005.999 7H9a1 1 0 010 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V3a1 1 0 011-1zm.008 9.057a1 1 0 011.276.61A5.002 5.002 0 0014.001 13H11a1 1 0 110-2h5a1 1 0 011 1v5a1 1 0 11-2 0v-2.101a7.002 7.002 0 01-11.601-2.566 1 1 0 01.61-1.276z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">Legacy Transformation</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">15-Year Systems Modernized</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-100 mb-3">
                  Critical legacy systems transformed without downtime, risk, or massive rewrites.
                </p>
                <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">
                  <div class="flex justify-between mb-1">
                    <span>Traditional Rewrite:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold">2-3 years, high risk</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>Greenfield Transformation:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-blue-400">3-6 months, zero risk</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-blue-200 text-sm">
                "We modernized our core banking system without a single minute of downtime." - Michael Rodriguez, CTO
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Enterprise Scale -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900 to-purple-800 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">Enterprise Scale</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">30k+ Users, Zero Issues</h3>
                <p class="text-purple-100 mb-3">
                  Complex enterprise systems handling massive scale with perfect reliability.
                </p>
                <div class="text-sm text-purple-200 space-y-1">
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>Concurrent Users:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-purple-400">30,000+</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>System Uptime:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-purple-400">99.99%</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>Development Teams:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-purple-400">25 teams</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-purple-200 text-sm">
                "25 teams working independently, zero conflicts, perfect coordination." - Jennifer Liu, Engineering Director
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Developer Experience -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-900 to-orange-800 rounded-lg p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400">Developer Experience</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="bg-black bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">100x Productivity Gains</h3>
                <p class="text-yellow-100 mb-3">
                  Developers report feeling like they have superpowers. Features that took weeks now take hours.
                </p>
                <div class="text-sm text-yellow-200 space-y-1">
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>Feature Development:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-yellow-400">100x faster</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>Bug Fixes:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-yellow-400">90% fewer bugs</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span>Onboarding Time:</span>
                    <span class="font-bold text-yellow-400">Days vs months</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-yellow-200 text-sm">
                "I've been coding for 15 years. This is the first time I've felt truly productive." - Alex Thompson, Senior Developer
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Case Studies Section -->
        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Detailed Case Studies</h2>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-lg p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400">E-commerce Platform: 0 to Production in 5 Days</h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2">Day 1-2</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">User authentication, payment processing, product catalog</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2">Day 3-4</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">Shopping cart, order management, admin dashboard</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2">Day 5</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">Production deployment, first customer orders</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                A complete e-commerce platform with all essential features, deployed to production and processing
                real orders in less than a week. What traditionally takes 6-12 months.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-lg p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-400">Healthcare System: Legacy Modernization</h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2">Challenge</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">15-year-old patient management system, critical to operations, impossible to rewrite</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2">Solution</h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">Bounded contexts gradually absorbed functionality, zero downtime transformation</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                The legacy system continues running while new bounded contexts handle new features and gradually
                take over old ones. Zero risk, continuous operation, modern architecture.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to See How It Works?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
              Dive deep into the technical architecture that makes these results possible.
            </p>
            <div class="space-x-4">
              <a href="/platform" class="inline-block bg-white text-green-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors">
                Explore the Platform
              </a>
              <a href="/start" class="inline-block border-2 border-white text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">
                Get Started Now
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>